KeysToEntries.story_2_1_005:
From the start,
you punks were
out of my sight.
KeysToEntries.story_2_1_004:
It’s not about disrespect…
it’s a whole other level.
KeysToEntries.story_2_1_003:
What’s that…?
You think we’re a joke?
KeysToEntries.story_2_1_000:
Heh heh… sorry,
ended up picking on
the weak.
KeysToEntries.story_2_1_001:
And you talk big\ just ‘cause you
landed a cheap shot…?
KeysToEntries.story_2_1_002:
We can go again,
I don’t care.
